title: Slide

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for an “slide,” as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a perspective view of an “slide” showing my new design;
FIG. 2 is a front view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a rear view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a left side view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a right side view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a top view thereof;
FIG. 7 is a bottom view thereof; and,
FIG. 8 is a zipper in use after a puller is assembled on the zipper.
It being understood that the broken lines of the zipper pull are for illustrative purposes only and form no part of the claimed design.
